---
title: Vegan Broccoli & Sun-Dried Tomato Pasta with Zucchini, Shallot & Fresh Parsley
description: Spotlight on all the vegans and veggie-lovers in the house—it’s pasta night! This garden-inspired meal is so flavorful and satisfying, you’ll wonder why all pasta isn’t topped with a bevy of delicious produce. Our spin on classic penne with tomato sauce is studded with garlicky zucchini and umami-rich sun-dried tomatoes. Top your bowl with a savory pile of oven-roasted broccoli and caramelized shallot, and sprinkle with chopped fresh parsley for an herbaceous touch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vegan-broccoli-sun-dried-tomato-pasta-aff93e3d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/vegan-broccoli-sun-dried-tomato-pasta-63fe3918fe58f1966d02aded-03544307.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/vegan-broccoli-sun-dried-tomato-pasta-63fe3918fe58f1966d02aded
nutrition:
  calories: 610 kcal
  fat: 12 g
  saturated fat: 2 g
  carbohydrates: 108 g
  sugar: 30 g
  protein: 22 g
  fiber: 13 g
  sodium: 880 mg
